	<legis-body id="HE647FD1583F345C28C4C000F60AAAB37" style="OLC">
 <section id="HA39E90ABF13B471BB0E0BADBCC8A996B" section-type="section-one"><enum>1.</enum><header>Short title</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote><short-title>Federal Transit Modernization Act of 2017</short-title></quote>.</text> </section><section id="H1B8D64DB0AFE49CD86B70F355C105F7A"><enum>2.</enum><header>Employee protective arrangements</header> <subsection id="H3590B87F1FAA4AD7A15E68EC95B64B49"><enum>(a)</enum><header>In general</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Section 5333 of title 49, United States Code, is amended—</text>
 <paragraph id="H2B4269CC37F641F89464C169E9B40833"><enum>(1)</enum><text>by striking <quote>(a) <header-in-text level="subsection" style="USC">Prevailing wages requirement.—</header-in-text></quote>; and</text> </paragraph><paragraph id="H9B7B7362EDA642F982448459D17C69DD"><enum>(2)</enum><text>by striking subsection (b).</text>
				</paragraph></subsection><subsection id="HA345E8C6824C47CBA6D4291EFD50F480"><enum>(b)</enum><header>Conforming amendments</header>
 <paragraph id="H56DBD17F8E054969BE163106D7D854B6"><enum>(1)</enum><header>Formula grants for rural areas</header><text>Section 5311(i) of title 49, United States Code, is repealed.</text> </paragraph><paragraph id="H2475C3A70B69432A9764AB2BFC7BE95C"><enum>(2)</enum><header>Administrative provisions</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Section 5334(a)(1) of title 49, United States Code, is amended by striking <quote>(except terms the Secretary of Labor prescribes under section 5333(b) of this title)</quote>.</text>
				</paragraph></subsection></section></legis-body></bill>


